    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "The putrid stench emanating from the catoblepas antlers adorning this *+2 greater striking greater crushing maul* interferes with your sense of smell. While wielding this weapon, you gain a +2 item bonus to saves against olfactory effects.",
